<paragraph id="8BF636D5697A7A2DDDA82F6507B5FB2A" blockId="14.[163,1070,1086,1166]" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">
C o m m e n t 
<taxonomicName id="4C494D56697A7A2DDC5B2F650740FBF7" baseAuthorityName="SHARP" baseAuthorityYear="1874" box="[336,520,1086,1107]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Rugilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="185" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufescens">
<emphasis id="B93DEAC7697A7A2DDC5B2F650740FBF7" box="[336,520,1086,1107]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">Rugilus rufescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is widespread in the East Palaearctic and Oriental regions, from 
<collectingCountry id="F35E7645697A7A2DDC322F000425FBD5" box="[313,365,1115,1137]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">India</collectingCountry>
to Kamchatka, 
<collectingCountry id="F35E7645697A7A2DDF132F07071CFBD5" box="[536,596,1116,1137]" name="Japan" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">Japan</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry id="F35E7645697A7A2DDF9B2F0007BFFBD5" box="[656,759,1115,1137]" name="Singapore" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">Singapore</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFD84B24697A7A2DDE032F0006E8FBD5" author="ASSING V" box="[776,928,1115,1137]" pageId="14" pageNumber="185" pagination="115 - 190" refId="ref11068" refString="ASSING V. (2012 a): The Rugilus species of the Palaearctic and Oriental regions (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 5: 115 - 190." type="journal article" year="2012">ASSING 2012a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD84B24697A7A2DDEA52F0006BAFBD5" author="ASSING V" box="[942,1010,1115,1137]" pageId="14" pageNumber="185" pagination="137 - 149" refId="ref11108" refString="ASSING V. (2012 b): A revision of Palaearctic and Oriental Rugilus LEACH, 1819. II. Three new species from China and additional records (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Koleopterologische Rundschau 82: 137 - 149." type="journal article" year="2012">2012b</bibRefCitation>
). The above specimens from 
<collectingCountry id="F35E7645697A7A2DDC872F2204F5FB2A" box="[396,445,1145,1166]" name="Laos" pageId="14" pageNumber="185">Laos</collectingCountry>
